      "topic": "Take Interventions",
      "micro_intent": "take_procedures",
      "role": "Partner",
      "utterance": "I noticed RFD already applied a C-spine manual stabilization and a cervical collar. Good form from the responders."
    },
    {
      "turn": 54,
      "topic": "Take Interventions",
      "micro_intent": "take_procedures",
      "role": "EMT",
      "utterance": "Checking the collar alignment. It appears to be supporting your neck well."
    },
    {
      "turn": 55,
      "topic": "Reassessments",
      "micro_intent": "retake_vital_signs - pulse",
      "role": "Partner",
      "utterance": "Pulse is now at 112, still strong. Any change in how you're feeling, Rachel?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 56,
      "topic": "Reassessments",
      "micro_intent": "retake_vital_signs - resp",
      "role": "Partner",
      "utterance": "Respiration rate remains 24, still non-labored."
    },
    {
      "turn": 57,
      "topic": "Reassessments",
      "micro_intent": "retake_vital_signs - bp",
      "role": "Partner",
      "utterance": "Blood pressure is 150 over 70. Good improvement from earlier."
    },
    {
      "turn": 58,
      "topic": "Reassessments",
      "micro_intent": "retake_vital_signs - spo2",
      "role": "Partner",
      "utterance": "O2 saturations: 97%, consistent with before."
    },
    {
      "turn": 59,
      "topic": "Reassessments",
      "micro_intent": "take_procedures",
      "role": "EMT",
      "utterance": "Let's check your neck again. That collar still fit well?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 60,
      "topic": "Reassessments",
      "micro_intent": "take_procedures",
      "role": "Patient",
      "utterance": "It's in place, a bit snug but okay."
    },
    {
      "turn": 61,
      "topic": "Secondary Assessment",
      "micro_intent": "midline_tenderness",
      "role": "Paramedic",
      "utterance": "Let me gently palpate your neck for midline tenderness. Does that hurt?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 62,
      "topic": "Secondary Assessment",
      "micro_intent": "midline_tenderness",
      "role": "Patient",
      "utterance": "A little. Especially in the middle."
    },
    {
      "turn": 63,
      "topic": "Secondary Assessment",
      "micro_intent": "ekg",
      "role": "EMT",
      "utterance": "We're noting you for EKG monitoring as part of the trauma protocol. I'll add a note for the hospital to follow up on this."
    },
    {
      "turn": 64,
      "topic": "Exit to Protocol",
      "micro_intent": "decide_ems_protocol",
      "role": "EMT",
      "utterance": "Per the assessment, we're coding this under injury protocol-general trauma management."
    },
    {
      "turn": 65,
      "topic": "Transport",
      "micro_intent": "destination_decision",
      "role": "EMT",
      "utterance": "Any particular hospital in mind for your care today?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 66,
      "topic": "Transport",
      "micro_intent": "destination_decision",
      "role": "Patient",
      "utterance": "Yes. I want to go to Chippenham Hospital."
    },
    {
      "turn": 67,
      "topic": "Transport",
      "micro_intent": "movement_secured",
      "role": "EMT",
      "utterance": "Moving carefully now. Just pivot into the stretcher slowly with me. Let's be gentle with your neck."
    },
    {
      "turn": 68,
      "topic": "Transport",
      "micro_intent": "movement_secured",
      "role": "Patient",
      "utterance": "Okay, go ahead. Just please be careful with my neck."
    },
    {
      "turn": 69,
      "topic": "Transport",
      "micro_intent": "movement_secured",
      "role": "Partner",
      "utterance": "Positioned and secured. Ready for the ambulance transport."
    },
    {
      "turn": 70,
      "topic": "Transport",
      "micro_intent": "movement_secured",
      "role": "EMT",
      "utterance": "All set. Let's get you inside and settled."
    },
    {
      "turn": 71,
      "topic": "Handoff",
      "micro_intent": "care_over_to_er",
      "role": "Paramedic",
      "utterance": "Nurse at Chippenham, we are en route with a 32-year-old with neck trauma and numbness due to a car accident."
    },
    {
      "turn": 72,
      "topic": "Handoff",
      "micro_intent": "anxiety_symptoms",
      "role": "EMT",
      "utterance": "Pt was anxious after the accident with initial hyperventilation. Improving now following Albuterol use."
